notes.text: Finish Challenge assignment and async work

notes.title: Drink More Water
notes.text: Do not forget to drink water throughout the day!!

notes.title: Exercise
notes.text: Try to incorporate 30 minutes of exercise each day.

notes.title: Breathe
notes.text: Take a moment and breathe when you are stressed.

notes.title: Don't Fixate
notes.text: When stuck on something for a long time take a step back and move on...  You can always come back to it!
